        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Buying Tip</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">The deluxe board often goes on sale during Black Friday and Amazon Prime Day. The <span class="text-white font-medium">Winning Solutions</span> brand is the most popular, but <span class="text-white font-medium">WS Game Company</span> makes a luxury version with real hardwood for $150+.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Travel Scrabble Board</h2>

      <p>Travel editions sacrifice size for portability. The best ones use magnetic tiles or snap-fit grids so you can play anywhere without losing pieces.</p>

