        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✓ Pros</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Compact and lightweight. Tiles stay put on bumpy surfaces. Folds flat for packing. Affordable. Self-contained storage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
          <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✗ Cons</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Small tiles hard to read. Limited table presence. Magnetic versions can be finicky. Not great for 4 players.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Best for: travelers, couples who play on the go, camping trips, hospital visits, or anyone who wants Scrabble without needing a full table.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Giant Outdoor Board</h2>

      <p>Giant Scrabble transforms the game into a social event. These oversized boards work perfectly for garden parties, barbecues, and family gatherings where you want a centerpiece activity.</p>

