        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Original 1948–1953 Scrabble sets by Selchow & Righter can fetch <span class="text-white font-medium">$200–$500+</span> in good condition. Verify authenticity before buying — check for the original manufacturer name, wooden tiles (not plastic), and the maroon/cream color scheme.</p>
      </div>

